---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="BrandStrategy">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="title">01. Brand Strategy</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="content">
                <p>This is the discover and strategy part.</p>
                <p>Questions:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Who is { AppConfig.brand_name }?</li>
                    <li>Who do you serve?</li>
                    <li>Why do you exist?</li>
                    <li>What makes you different?</li>
                    <li>How should people feel about you?</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <p>{ AppConfig.brand_name } is a software company.</p>
                <p>Target Audience: SMEs, Startups, Enterprises.</p>
                <p>Mission: Build custom software that helps businesses solve visibility (websites), management (management systems), branding (brand & visual design).</p>
                <p>Vision: Become the world's most trusted custom software company.</p>
                <p>Values: Innovation, Reliablity, Simplicity, Growth.</p>
                <p>Brand Personality: Intelligent, Modern, Professional, Approachable.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
